metadata.title: Sanpanpai Neckband Headphones, Earphones with TF Card Slot, IPX5 Sport Earbuds for Running, in-Ear Headset Lightweight Earphones - Black
features: 【Hi-Fi hd stereo】---Bt 5.0 & advanced chip technology and innovative acoustic design provide richer deep bass and high-fidelity, ultra-clear sound. Neckband Bt headset is compatible with most smartphones (iOS or Android system), tablet computers, TVs, etc., immerse yourself in the world of music!

【Waterproof & Sweat-proof】 --- IPX5 waterproof grade and internal hydrophobic nano-coated Bt headset can effectively resist sweat or rain, very suitable for running, mountaineering, hiking, gym fitness, travel, etc

【Magnetic design & Durable】 ---Super soft and lightweight material, slightly curved neckline, easy to store, become a fashionable necklace.This headset supports up to 8 hours of music or hands-free calling/150 hours of standby time. (Prerequisite: Please fully char-ge for 1.5 hours before use)

【CVC noise cancelling mic】---Bt headsets are designed with noise canceling microphones, which perfectly filter background noise. It can also capture your voice well when answering the phone while driving, cycling or running.

【No-Worry Warranty】 ---All earbuds are covered with 1 month worry-free warranty. Just simply drop us an email with your order number and we will give you the best solution as your wishes within 24hours
description: Bt Headphones Specifications: Bt version: 5.0 Range: 10m Bt Headphones In-ear Earbuds 10 hours Playback for Workout,Travel,Gym and more  IPX5 Waterproof  IPX5 sweat and water resistance, protects the headphones from heavy rains or sweat, enjoy your favorite music when running,gym workout, hiking, cycling and other exercises.  Comfortable Fit For Any Sport  The ergonomic design allows you to find the perfect choice for listening to music, away from outside noise, and the neckline ensures stability and comfort to wear, even in the midst of intense exercise without risk of loss.  The package includes: 1 headset 1 x USB cable （Note: TF card not included）
